\f4 \cf0 xp_publish.php
\f1 : this is the file from release 1.3.2 of Coppermine, already with the necessary modifications. Simply replace the existing 
\f4 xp_publish.php
\f1  file in your Coppermine installation directory with this one.\
\

\f4 xp_publish.php.cpg132.patch
\f1 : is a patch file containing the necessary changes (only 3 lines need to be changed). Copy the file to your Coppermine installation directory, log into the Coppermine server and run the following commands:\
\

\f4 cd /your/coppermine/directory\
patch -p0 < xp_publish.php.cpg132.patch
\f1 \
\
