\f4 xp_publish.php
\f1 .\
In both cases, make sure you make a copy of the original 
\f4 xp_publish.php
\f1  file before making any changes, so you can revert to it if anything goes wrong.\
\
The changes to 
\f4 xp_publish.php
\f1  do not affect the capability of uploading things from Windows XP.
